text: "La Carcacha" () is a song by American singer Selena. The music video became Selena's first music video, which was released in 1992. The song also helped Selena to tour in Mexico and reached within the top ten of Billboards Hot Latin Tracks chart. Category:Selena songs Category:1992 songs Category:Songs written by A.B. Quintanilla Category:Songs in Spanish
title: La Carcacha
